{
  "stem": "11175.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they-- then they-- after the selection, they took the older people which they selected to be gassed in the other Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the rest, we remained in the-- sitting on the-- on the ground.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they picked up people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stood up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I accidentally said I'm a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A carpenter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was young, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this side, the-- the other more older people with women, they put on a different side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they selected this-- the group which they have to go back to the-- to the Treblinka for the gassing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were-- put them together and they marched-- marched them away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They march them over to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we found out this group, you see, in the morning, they had to take him a group to Malchin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a station, Malchin, to Malchin to work there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also the coal, [INAUDIBLE], doing all kind of work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Instead, to bring him back, these people which they took out from the Treblinka where I was there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead to bring them back there, they took them straight down to the ovens, and they liquidate them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't see-- so there, they prepared some food for them, the cook, the soup, whatever there us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this soup and this everything, that this group what remains there sitting on the-- on the-- on the ground, when they left for the other Treblinka for the liquidation, so they took us into a barrack.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Already. ?] This barrack was known as the death barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was it called in German?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so this-- the-- the people, which they are supposed to come back and the stay there, they didn't came back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took them right there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
